<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men shì hé yī de, wǒ men shì bǐ cǐ xiāng ài de.
 wǒ men shì chōng mǎn xìn xīn de, wǒ men shì chōng mǎn pàn wàng de.
 ài shǐ wǒ men xiāng jù zài yī qǐ, ài shǐ wǒ men xiāng jù zài yī qǐ.
 měi hǎo de shì qíng yī dìng huì fā shēng, yīn yé sū zài zhè lǐ.
 yīn yé sū zài zhè lǐ.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men shì hé yī de 迦南1129</title>
